&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic individual to join our friendly and supportive Orthodontic / Oral maxillofacial team. You must be able to demonstrate good communication skills and be able to work well within a team environment. You will be responsible for providing high standards of preventative oral health education and pre and post-operative support to a wide variety of patient’s. Previous experience of providing patient care within a health setting would be advantageous. 6 month temporary contract with the hope of extending.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information or an informal visit please contact Sarah Thorpe or Joshua Egginton (01709) 428168&lt;/p&gt;
